Añadir subcambio en Firebase (subcolección)


Ejemplo — Añadir fotos adicionales a una fuente
Queremos guardar múltiples fotos por fuente en: fountains/{id}/photos

Subcambio 1 — Modelo Photo.kt
📄  Photo.kt
data class Photo(
    val id: String = "",
    val url: String = "",
    val uploadedBy: String = "",
    val timestamp: Long = System.currentTimeMillis()
)


Subcambio 2 — Repository: leer y guardar fotos
📄  FirebaseFountainRepository.kt — añadir métodos
// GUARDAR foto en subcolección:
suspend fun addPhoto(fountainId: String, photo: Photo): Result<Unit> {
    return try {
        val ref = db.collection("fountains").document(fountainId)
                    .collection("photos").document()
        ref.set(photo.copy(id = ref.id)).await()
        Result.success(Unit)
    } catch (e: Exception) {
        Result.failure(e)
    }
}

// LEER fotos de la subcolección:
fun fetchPhotos(fountainId: String): Flow<Result<List<Photo>>> = callbackFlow {
    val sub = db.collection("fountains").document(fountainId)
        .collection("photos")
        .orderBy("timestamp")
        .addSnapshotListener { snapshot, error ->
            if (error != null) {
                trySend(Result.failure(error))
            } else {
                val photos = snapshot?.documents?.mapNotNull {
                    it.toObject(Photo::class.java)?.copy(id = it.id)
                } ?: emptyList()
                trySend(Result.success(photos))
            }
        }
    awaitClose { sub.remove() }
}

// BORRAR foto:
suspend fun deletePhoto(fountainId: String, photoId: String): Result<Unit> {
    return try {
        db.collection("fountains").document(fountainId)
            .collection("photos").document(photoId)
            .delete().await()
        Result.success(Unit)
    } catch (e: Exception) { Result.failure(e) }
}


Subcambio 3 — UseCase
📄  FetchPhotosUseCase.kt
class FetchPhotosUseCase @Inject constructor(
    private val repository: FountainRepository
) {
    operator fun invoke(fountainId: String) = repository.fetchPhotos(fountainId)
}

class AddPhotoUseCase @Inject constructor(
    private val repository: FountainRepository
) {
    suspend operator fun invoke(fountainId: String, photo: Photo) =
        repository.addPhoto(fountainId, photo)
}


Subcambio 4 — ViewModel
📄  DetailFountainViewModel.kt o nuevo PhotoViewModel.kt
@HiltViewModel
class PhotoViewModel @Inject constructor(
    private val fetchPhotosUseCase: FetchPhotosUseCase,
    private val addPhotoUseCase: AddPhotoUseCase
) : ViewModel() {

    var photos by mutableStateOf<List<Photo>>(emptyList())
        private set

    fun loadPhotos(fountainId: String) {
        viewModelScope.launch {
            fetchPhotosUseCase(fountainId).collect { result ->
                result.onSuccess { photos = it }
            }
        }
    }

    fun addPhoto(fountainId: String, url: String, userId: String) {
        viewModelScope.launch {
            val photo = Photo(url = url, uploadedBy = userId)
            addPhotoUseCase(fountainId, photo)
        }
    }
}


